					(thickness 0.15)
				)
			)
		)
		(property "Description" "Codec TX series-R / OUTP abs-max protection (2.2k): OUTP -> R26 -> C14 -> TALK_BRIDGE. Series R at the codec output pin limits the ES8311 OUTP ESD-clamp current when K1's make steps +12V (P2) onto TALK_BRIDGE and C14 couples that edge back to OUTP - keeps OUTP inside the analog abs-max [AGND-0.3, AVDD+0.3] (sim invariant B1). Also isolates the DAC output from the C14 load; TX level is gain-recoverable (codec digital volume)."
			(at 0 0 0)
			(unlocked yes)
			(layer "F.Fab")
			(hide yes)
			(uuid "396f872e-db46-44ae-b263-676846238ae4")
